00:17:49.427 --> 00:17:50.885 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's
informing the field.

00:17:50.885 --> 00:17:53.360 align:middle line:84%
>>FREKE: It's informing
what's happening now,

00:17:53.360 --> 00:17:55.770 align:middle line:84%
