00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:15.110 align:middle line:90%
How can I get back there?

00:20:15.110 --> 00:20:16.430 align:middle line:90%
How can I understand it?

00:20:16.430 --> 00:20:17.900 align:middle line:90%
How can I cultivate it?

00:20:17.900 --> 00:20:19.570 align:middle line:90%
And then how can I share it?

00:20:19.570 --> 00:20:21.700 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So have you
gotten back there?

00:20:21.700 --> 00:20:25.140 align:middle line:84%
>>FREKE: All the time, but not
in some oh, I'm enlightened--

00:20:25.140 --> 00:20:27.410 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Not in this
profound, out of control, way.

00:20:27.410 --> 00:20:29.530 align:middle line:84%
>>FREKE: One thing I'm
